com.badlogic.gdx.ai.btree.annotation

Annotation Type TaskConstraint


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Inherited
 @Documented
public @interface TaskConstraint
    This annotation specifies how many children the task can have. It is applied to the task class.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      int maxChildren
      Returns the maximum number of allowed children, defaults to Integer.MAX_VALUE.
      int minChildren
      Returns the minimum number of allowed children, defaults to 0.
